{"title":"升旗仪式","authors":["柯愈勋"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":6,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"升旗仪式"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柯愈勋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗，上升，上升"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天空，辽阔起来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燃烧是一种颜色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为清凉的晨风所鼓荡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是，展示风的姿态"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝天——大写意"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每天，我们都以"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整齐的队列，行注目礼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"内心，则升起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一种向上的精神"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗呵火焰呵祖国呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有阳光霞光目光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都在想：天空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么辽阔而深邃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"目光一旦燃烧起来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也会升华为——旗……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}